tables.table_schema:
CREATE TABLE employee_work_logs (
    employee_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    log_date DATE,
    log_start_time TIME,
    log_end_time TIME,
    work_hours DECIMAL(5,2)
)

CREATE TABLE Timesheets (
  timesheet_id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
  employee_id INT,
  start_date DATE,
  end_date DATE,
  total_hours DECIMAL
);

CREATE TABLE employee_work_logs (
    log_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    employee_id INT,
    log_date DATE,
    hours_worked DECIMAL(5,2),
    task_description TEXT
);

CREATE TABLE employee_timesheets (
    timesheet_id INT PRIMARY KEY,

    start_date DATE,
    end_date DATE,
    total_hours DECIMAL(5,2)
);

CREATE TABLE work_logs ( log_id INT PRIMARY KEY, employee_id INT, log_date DATE, hours_worked DECIMAL(5,2) )
CREATE TABLE timesheets ( timesheet_id INT PRIMARY KEY, employee_id INT, start_date DATE, end_date DATE, total_hours DECIMAL(5,2) )
